INNER JOIN user_detail AS u ON CASE
    WHEN m.sender_id = @__userId_0 THEN m.recipient_id
    ELSE m.sender_id
END = u.user_id
WHERE m.sender_id = @__userId_0 OR m.recipient_id = @__userId_0
